data.description: WOW! Country living at its best! This lovely 3 bedroom 2 Bathroom home sitting on a 1.1 acre fenced property with electric entry gate is ready for your enjoyment.  This home was built in 2018, owner is first ever resident here from January 2021, so the home still looks practically new. Come enjoy the Fresh Air, Star Filled Nights, and the Fantastic Views from most of the property but especially from the wrap around covered porch. The gorgeous electric gate at the property entrance is followed up by a nice gravel circular driveway leading to the front of the home.  The property has plenty of room for RV and practically any toys you can imagine.  There is a very productive private well which was dug in 2019 with a 5000 gallon steel water tank and a fire hydrant on the property. Also there is a 12' x 10' shed/well house for well equipment and extra storage. The sceptic system and tank were installed at time of construction. There is a 250 gallon propane tank.
